                <head>No. 1541<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>Telegram 212 from Jidda, November 9, reported the death of King <persName
                        corresp="#p_ISAA1">Ibn Saud</persName> and the accession to the throne of
                    Crown Prince <persName corresp="#p_SIAA1">Saud</persName>. For additional
                    information, see telegram 218 from Jidda, <ref target="#d1458">Document
                        1458</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
